                                Cincinnati Chili

1 lb    ground meat                     1 oz    unsweetened chocolate
        onion                           1/2 tsp cumin
        garlic                          1/2 tsp turmeric
1 c     tomato sauce                    1/2 tsp marjoram
2 Tbsp  ketchup                         1/2 tsp allspice
1 c     water                           1/2 tsp cinnamon
1 Tbsp  red wine vinegar                1/2 tsp nutmeg
1 Tbsp  chili powder                    1/4 tsp cloves
1 Tbsp  paprika                         1/4 tsp mace
1 tsp   black pepper                    1/4 tsp coriander
1 tsp   honey                           1/4 tsp cardamom
1   tsp salt                                bay leaf

Brown meat with onion and garlic.
Add tomato sauce, ketchup, water, and vinegar.
As mixture boils, add spices.
Simmer for 1 hour.
